11. TERMINATION
================================================================================

11.1 AUTOMATIC TERMINATION
--------------------------------------------------------------------------------
Your rights terminate automatically if you violate this license in Public 
Distribution context, including:
- Removing AOL license headers from AOL files
- Failing to comply with attribution requirements
- Relicensing without meeting Section 5 conditions

11.2 EFFECT OF TERMINATION
--------------------------------------------------------------------------------
Upon termination:
- You must cease all Public Distribution
- Personal Use rights continue
- Limited Sharing rights continue (if violation was only Public 
  Distribution-related)
- Compliant copies you distributed remain valid
- Downstream recipients' rights are unaffected

11.3 REINSTATEMENT
--------------------------------------------------------------------------------
Rights may be reinstated if you:
1. Cure the violation within 30 days of notice
2. Provide written confirmation of compliance

